**BCMonster.com**, also known as **Bitcoin Monster**, is a [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]] that allows mining bitcoins (BTC).  It is one of the newest pool on the bitcoin pool scene with a very easy to use dashboard. BCMonster.com is based in the United States.   

The [[coinbase]] signature for this pool is: "/BCMonster/"  (1.1). 

##Reward distribution

* 0.5% fee PPLNS 
* Payout available as soon as a block is confirmed with 101 confirmations.
* Transaction fees paid to the miners.

##Extra Features

* [[Stratum]] support with merge mining
* IRC channel #bcmonster on the freenode network
* Support via email 
